Scalactic/ScalaTest 3.2.16 is a point release that makes a few enhancements.
Changes included:
Added overridable differ to Prettifier trait, and added functions to create prettifier instance with supplied Differ. (
#2221
).
Recognize -S as a valid argument in checkArgsForValidity, used by Runner. (
#2222
).
Deprecated NoArg as scala.DelayedInit is dropped from Scala 3, updated ScalaDoc. (
#2228
).
Fixed compiler warning in expanded code when the size or length method call contains empty bracket. (
#2230
).
Fixed "SuiteAborted.this.message was null" error (
#2236
).
Thanks to the contributors for the Scalactic/ScalaTest 3.2.16 release:
